abstract: >-
  This technical note proposes DynamicSLM, a capability-modular and self-improving small language model architecture for AIKernel. DynamicSLM defines model artifacts through an AIKernel Model ABI and enables dynamic capability loading, capability-level differential distillation, and hot-swappable runtime scheduling under AIKernel governance. This work is conceptual and architectural in nature; it does not present empirical benchmarks.
